                  <colophon xml:id="coloph1">
                     <locus target="#83r">83r</locus>: ይትባረክ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘአፈጸመኒ፡ በደኅና፡ ወበሰላም፡ በ፲ወ፱፻፲
                     ወ፫፡ ኮነ፡ ዓመተ፡ ዓለም፡ ወለጸሐፊሁ፡ ኃጥእ፡ ወአባሲ፡ ኪዳነ፡ ማርያም።<locus target="#83r">83r</locus>: May God be blessed who caused me to complete (it) in health and
                     in peace in 1913 year of the world. And his scribe sinner and trespasser Kidāna
                     Māryām.  According to the colophon the Ms. was completed in 1913 “year of the
                     world” which most likely should be interpreted as the “year of mercy”. 1913
                     year of mercy corresponds to 1920/21 A.D. The scribe of the Ms. is Kidāna
                     Māryām. </colophon>
               </msContents>
